    "name_suffix": "_v2-2025",
    "display_name": "Bucket Pickup",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Right now, the `Painter` only knows what to do if it finds a paint bucket, but doesn't handle what to do when there's *no* bucket. Help the `Painter` make smarter decisions by adding an `else` block so it can keep moving, even when there's nothing to pick up.",
